about.summary: Quick grid visualization and conversion to GIS formats.

name: gridgeo
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "0.2.1" %}

package:
    name: gridgeo
    version: {{ version }}

source:
    fn: v{{ version }}.tar.gz
    url: https://github.com/pyoceans/gridgeo/archive/v{{ version }}.tar.gz
    sha256: 02c302fc3cd4ecb3702a96715563c3672db38dc764373a2b0eb7a5906a9388a2

build:
    number: 0
    script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record=record.txt

requirements:
    build:
        - python
        - setuptools
    run:
        - python
        - pyugrid
        - pysgrid
        - shapely
        - fiona

test:
    imports:
        - gridgeo

about:
    home: https://github.com/pyoceans/gridgeo
    license: MIT
    summary: 'Quick grid visualization and conversion to GIS formats.'

extra:
    recipe-maintainers:
        - ocefpaf
